{"tid":1957835,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美議員為病毒命名發起網上投票 「中共病毒」當選","createTime":"2020-04-04T07:41:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-04T12:49:49.000Z","uid":32511,"like":43,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"082abbe2b8f526a7c8fc920c82c64589509748f3","tid":1957835,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T07:41:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ntdtv.com/assets/uploads/2020/04/bb117ef531de967552729d627cd1f40e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ntdtv.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F04%2Fbb117ef531de967552729d627cd1f40e.jpg&h=771da286&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國亞利桑那州共和黨籍聯邦眾議員戈薩（Paul Gosar）日前宣布，他在網絡社交平台推特(twitter)上發起的一項給新型冠狀病毒命名的投票活動結束。有數萬網民參與了投票，而在4個備選的選項中，CCP virus以52%的得票率當選。<br />\n <br />\n戈薩於3月30日晚間在推特上發起這項命名活動時，列出了Wuhan virus；CCP virus；China virus；SARS COVID-19 Red death 這四個供投票者選擇的選項。到4月1日活動結束時，共有近3萬5千人參與，而CCP virus的得票率高達52%，得票率最低的選項是SARSCOVID-19 Red death，僅佔5% 。<br />\n <br />\n戈薩宣布這項票選活動結束時在推文中寫道，「 報票已經結束， 34253人參與投票。 從現在開始當我們談論這個新型冠狀病毒時，我們應該加上CCP virus 這個名稱。 謝謝幾千名參與投票的中國人，你們的留言告訴了我們為什麼CCP virus 是這種病毒準確的名稱。」<br />\n<br />\n有中國網友在自己的推特賬號中轉載了Paul Gosar 發起這項票選活動的推文，並發推文稱「謝謝議員先生發起這個投票，讓世界聽到中國人真正的聲音！」<br />\n <br />\n據了解，Paul Gosar是美國共和黨籍國會眾議員，代表亞利桑那州第四區。<br />\n <br />\n早在3月上旬，中共病毒開始在美國華盛頓州大爆發時，有人參與了美國保守聯盟(American Conservative Union)舉行的一次會議後，被確診感染了COVID-19。保守聯盟於3月7日公佈了這個消息。隨後，有7名曾接觸過這病患者的美國國會議員先後宣布主動進行自我隔離或觀察14天，其中就包括來自亞利桑那州眾議員保羅戈薩(Paul Gosar)。<br />\n <br />\n戈薩3月8日曾就此事發表聲明稱，他和他的三名工作人員曾與那名患者「在一起待了較長一段時間，還握了幾次手」。他說，他的辦公室將關閉一周，他們都將在亞利桑那州的家中自主隔離14天， 「我們都沒有癥狀，感覺很好，但我們要保持謹慎。」"},{"pid":"dbd8be93c3782b409d57af4e29a2c29a02d11626","tid":1957835,"uid":125168,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T07:44:40.000Z","msg":"謝謝幾千名參與投票的中國人，你們的留言告訴了我們為什麼CCP virus 是這種病毒準確的名稱。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e386dcd753c469003386bb0ea831634243e31d16","tid":1957835,"uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T07:45:20.000Z","msg":"why not  xi jinping virus <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62431d163c9673d36e857b950d1dd7a01fcd8db1","tid":1957835,"uid":254594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T07:46:25.000Z","msg":"3個都ok<br />\n同我心目中ranking一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e23ae991e7b9d7cfd6d90992c686b5e19080c2b","tid":1957835,"uid":125168,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e386dcd753c469003386bb0ea831634243e31d16","tid":1957835,"uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T07:45:20.000Z","msg":"why not  xi jinping virus <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T07:46:41.000Z","msg":"因為中共唔死邊個上位都一樣"},{"pid":"062cb075bcd7cf942c67def4a9358b4218acfe6d","tid":1957835,"uid":28068,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T07:46:55.000Z","msg":"d左膠食屎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac110d65efc6402e23222756787aeac4a6bcee29","tid":1957835,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T07:48:41.000Z","msg":"支那肺炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c44d620764ebc61eab6d38355109cfb486acb847","tid":1957835,"uid":144522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T07:48:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"104f57a78734cfc748fe7d1f783df36219b55ef8","tid":1957835,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T07:49:54.000Z","msg":"Chinese Virus<i